title: Group Therapy: Should She Reach Out to "Help" a Stranger?
description: Marta calls in because she found a girl on Instagram with tons of followers that she started to follow but has realized that this girl could use some help.  She posts a lot of lingerie pictures, is drinking all the time, should Marta try to help her or just let her live her life?
